nodes.text: The CorSec Database H-Z is the second part of the in-universe CorSec Database for Star Wars Galaxies gamers. It was published on June 16, 2006 on the Star Wars Galaxies official website.
The database accounts for the following non-player characters and organizations:
The database is a continuation of the first part, which accounts for A-G.
Like the first part of the database, CorSec Database H-Z is written from an in-universe perspective, but unlike the first part, the second part does not have any introductory or exit text.
